---
// About section component
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-16">
        About Me
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            I'm an aspiring web developer who builds websites and web applications for clients.
            I work with Astro and have experience with React and Laravel from my studies.
            Currently expanding into eCommerce development with Shopify.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            I focus on creating responsive, functional websites - from landing pages and
            business sites to portfolios and single-page applications. Always learning
            new technologies to improve my skills.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-purple-900 dark:to-blue-900 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Astro</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-purple-900 dark:to-blue-900 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">React</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-purple-900 dark:to-blue-900 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Laravel</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-purple-900 dark:to-blue-900 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Shopify</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-purple-900 dark:to-blue-900 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Responsive Design</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 p-1" style="aspect-ratio: 4/3;">
            <div class="w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
              <!-- Animated Code Snippets -->
              <div class="relative w-64 h-48 font-mono text-md leading-relaxed">
                <!-- React Code -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 code-snippet-1 opacity-0">
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">const <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">App</span> = &#40;&#41; =&gt; &#123;</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-4">return &#40;</div>
                  <div class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 ml-8">&lt;div className="app"&gt;</div>
                  <div class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 ml-12">Hello World</div>
                  <div class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 ml-8">&lt;/div&gt;</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-4">&#41;;</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">&#125;<span class="w-0.5 bg-purple-600 dark:bg-purple-400 cursor-blink ml-1" style="display: inline-block; height: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; top: 0.25em;"></span></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Astro Code -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 code-snippet-2 opacity-0">
                  <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">---</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">const <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">title</span> = 'Portfolio';</div>
                  <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">---</div>
                  <div class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">&lt;html&gt;</div>
                  <div class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 ml-4">&lt;title&gt;&#123;title&#125;&lt;/title&gt;</div>
                  <div class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">&lt;/html&gt;<span class="w-0.5 bg-purple-600 dark:bg-purple-400 cursor-blink ml-1" style="display: inline-block; height: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; top: 0.25em;"></span></div>
                </div>

                <!-- PHP/Laravel Code -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 code-snippet-3 opacity-0">
                  <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">&lt;?php</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Route::<span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">get</span>&#40;'/', function &#40;&#41; &#123;</div>
                  <div class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 ml-4">return view&#40;'welcome'&#41;;</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">&#125;&#41;;<span class="w-0.5 bg-purple-600 dark:bg-purple-400 cursor-blink ml-1" style="display: inline-block; height: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; top: 0.25em;"></span></div>
                </div>

                <!-- CSS Code -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 code-snippet-4 opacity-0">
                  <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">.container &#123;</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 ml-4">display: <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">flex</span>;</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 ml-4">justify-content: <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">center</span>;</div>
                  <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 ml-4">align-items: <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">center</span>;</div>
                  <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">&#125;<span class="w-0.5 bg-purple-600 dark:bg-purple-400 cursor-blink ml-1" style="display: inline-block; height: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; top: 0.25em;"></span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-900 rounded-full opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 bg-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-full opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What I Do Section -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          What I Do
        </h3>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Web Development</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Building responsive websites and web applications for clients - from single-page applications to multi-page sites, landing pages, business websites, and portfolios.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M8 11v6h8v-6M8 11H5.5A1.5 1.5 0 004 12.5v6A1.5 1.5 0 005.5 20H10"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">eCommerce Solutions</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Exploring eCommerce development with Shopify to help businesses establish their online presence and sell their products effectively.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Continuous Learning</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              Currently expanding my skills in mobile development and exploring backend technologies to become a more well-rounded developer.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInOut {
    0%, 20% { opacity: 1; }
    25%, 95% { opacity: 0; }
    100% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .code-snippet-1 {
    animation: fadeInOut 8s infinite;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .code-snippet-2 {
    animation: fadeInOut 8s infinite;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  .code-snippet-3 {
    animation: fadeInOut 8s infinite;
    animation-delay: 4s;
  }

  .code-snippet-4 {
    animation: fadeInOut 8s infinite;
    animation-delay: 6s;
  }

  .cursor-blink {
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
